api_list.name: Futures Expiration Calendar
api_list.description: This endpoint provides information about the futures expiration calendar.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://investing4.p.rapidapi.com/calendar/futures-expiration-calendar"

    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "investing4.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
